attributes.title: This app smells like rotten eggs
attributes.review: I kid you not, I opened this app and it proceeded to make my whole home smell like pungent rotten eggs. I thought maybe my dog had farted, so I went outside to try again. This time when I opened the app my entire block absolutely reeked!!! My neighbors called the police because they thought I was making a chemical weapon. Luckily when the swat team arrived, they saw that I was a white woman, told me to have a wonderful day, and left. So even though this app didnâ€™t get me arrested, I cannot recommend it.
